    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered like a member of the family. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! I'm only letting it go because I'm looking to downsize. If you're searching for something that's basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
