    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
