    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s benchmark, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing, and the rod bearings\u2014a critical preventative maintenance item\u2014have been addressed. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock for exceptional mechanical traction. The chassis is structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement, preserving the 50/50 weight distribution and torsional rigidity. The suspension remains tight, utilizing original geometry to provide the visceral, analog feedback modern EPS systems lack. This is a turn-key collector-grade example with zero mechanical parasitic loss and a flawless exterior finish.",
